captions.text: - You know what, we should go out.
- Yeah, we haven't done that in a while.

- Friday I'm supposed to go
out with the girls, remember?
- Did you just get out of the shower?
- Well, how much time are you gonna need?
- So are we eating inside or outside?
does the restaurant have heat lamps?
Why, you want me to call?
Do you guys have patio heaters?
- Oh, just let me go put on my shoes.
- I thought you said you were ready.
- I am ready, I just don't have shoes on.
- Well, we passed a bunch back there.
- I think I can find something closer.

- I just wanted to know
what my options were.
- I'm thinkin' the fish and chips.
- That's what I was gonna get.
- We both get fish and chips.
- No, we both can't get the same thing.

That defeats the purpose
of going out to dinner.
Then, I will get the bolognese,

you get the fish and chips,
and we'll go halfsies.
- Then we'll both get fish and chips.

- [Waiter] Here you go.
- Awesome, thank you.
Are you kidding me right now?

- All right, can I get you
guys anything for dessert?

- Yeah, nothing's going
inside these bellies.
- That's it, that's the end of my plans.
We could go to a bar?
We could go on a walk?
So what do you wanna do?
What do you think of these?
Thanks for a great date night.

- Aw, it doesn't have to end
there, if you know what I mean.
- Ooh, what do you have in mind?
- ♫ Close your eyes and make believe ♫

- (laughs) Will you take this
character into the bedroom?
